# Tauri Agentic Rules for collab-finder

- Backend (Rust): central hunter_reactor module with guards, MCP server (stdio or local HTTP), secure keyring for X/xAI keys, app_data_dir for state (JSON leads/preps).
- No direct X/xAI calls outside reactor.
- Capabilities: scope fs to app_data + approved devprofile_path only; dialog for exports/promotes.
- Frontend: minimal state, deliberate tauri invoke, command palette for agent actions, visual guard indicators (cost, rate, fit).
- MCP: expose search, analyze, prep, promote, get_state as tools; use pause responses for intervention.
- Integrate X resources: load .agents/x-resources/skill.md at startup for context.
- Follow tauri-agentic/SKILL.md + react-client-expert.
- Surplus for UI/UX improvements that make agent interaction cheaper.

Use with finder-reactor and fusion-sage.